msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh ho, I may not look it now, but I was\n"
"quite the traveler when I was young.\n"
"Quite a beauty, too!\n"
"It was a rare thing for a voe not to notice\n"
"me come into a room.\n"
"\n"
"But...I had a fairy-tale notion in my mind.<2.pa>\n"
"I'd heard of the <3.se_co>Lover's Pond<4.re_co>, and I\n"
"thought I'd meet my true love there.\n"
"I traveled all across Hyrule, searching for\n"
"this fabled place.<5.pa> But I couldn't find it...\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>And before I knew it, I'd grown old. <7.pa>The\n"
"voe no longer turned when I walked in.\n"
"\n"
"Oh, don't look so sad!<8.pa> I stopped being\n"
"sad about it a long time ago.<9.pa>\n"
"And I chased my dreams!"
msgstr ""

